Blog for the Department of Art History and Program for Urban Design and Architecture Studies at NYU. It includes announcements related to faculty, alumni, the Architecture Club, the Fine Arts Society, the Grey Art Gallery, the Institute for Fine Arts, Silsila lecture series, the Urban Design and Architecture Society, Ink and Image, admissions for the Historical and Sustainable Architecture MA in London, study abroad, and other events. The blog dates back to 2011.
